<div class="title">First Experience with Psychedelics</div>
<div class="substance">5-MeO-DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Crescent+Fresh&Exact=1">Crescent Fresh</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Crescent Fresh. "First Experience with Psychedelics: An Experience with 5-MeO-DMT (exp34672)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jul 8, 2004. erowid.org/exp/34672</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

